Package: multiOmicsVizEnhanced
Title: Enhanced Multi-Omics Correlation and Chromosomal Visualization Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Provides enhanced multi-omics correlation analysis and chromosome-based
 visualization. Extends the original 'multiOmicsViz' package with improved
 ggplot-based heatmaps, customizable aesthetics, simplified single-omics
 modes, and optimized parallel correlation computation.
